candidates<b> </b>- Albania, Bosnia and Herzegovina, Montenegro and Serbia, as well as Moldova and 
Ukraine), India, Japan, Malaysia, Mexico, Morocco, Norway* (also on behalf of Denmark, 
Finland, Iceland and Sweden), Pakistan (on behalf of the Organization of the Islamic 
